items.badge_description: At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 300 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 61! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 130 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 27!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 45 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 10!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 75 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 16.

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 35 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 8! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
